summary: This is a complete new retexture for Male and Femal Khajiits (2048)
descriptionHtml:
This is a complete new retexture for Male and Femal Khajiits
There are two Versions!

IVNM = Improved Vanilla Normal Map (So they aren\'t Blocky and at 2048)

CNM = Custom Normal Map (Complete new Normal Maps with a bit less Grand Canyon look)

For more Questions and how to Install, please read the Readme.

Edit:
Now with Pictures without FXAA
